high_descs: Turn right, go forward, turn right. Exit the room. When you leave the room, turn left. Continue to the countertop. Turn right, stop at the countertop.
Grab the egg.
Turn right. Go ahead and turn right and stand in front of the diningtable.
Place the egg on the left, near the diningtable.
Turn around. Go ahead and turn left. Reach the fridge and turn left until you are in front of the shelf with doors.
Open the egg door. Take out the potato. Close the door.
Turn around, move forward. Turn to the right. Turn right when you reach the diningtable. Move closer.
Place the egg to the left, before the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Search for eggs. Bring them to the dining table with the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and exit the room, then turn left and walk toward the kitchen ahead; face the countertop.
Pick up the egg on the counter by sink.
Turn around on your back of your right side there is a diningtable, walk toward there and face it.
Put the egg on the diningtable in front of the control panel of the microwave.
Turn around and walk around the wall on your left and there is a fridge; walk toward it.
Open the refrigerator, pick up the egg next to the fry pan; close refrigerator when done.
Turn around and walk around the diningtable on your right to go back to microwave.
Put the egg on the diningtable in front of the other egg.
anns.task_desc: Place two Egg on the DiningTable.

high_descs: Turn and walk to the countertop in the kitchen room.
Pick up the egg.
Turn around right  and left
Go to the diningtable.
Put the egg in the fridge and turn around to go to the fridge.
Open the fridge and move to the egg.
Turn around and go to the diningtable.
Put the egg in the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Pick up the egg, open the fridge, move to the egg, put the egg on the dining table.
